data.title: Former Presidents of UN Climate Talks Call for Strong Outcome at COP24
data.meta_description: Former Presidents of UN Climate Talks Call for Strong Outcome at COP24: Manuel Pulgar-Vidal, leader of WWF’s global climate and energy practice and former President of COP20, joins with three former COP presidents in issuing a ‘call to arms’ as the COP24 UN climate summit opens in Katowice, Polan
data.text: Former Presidents of UN Climate Talks Call for Strong Outcome at COP24: Manuel Pulgar-Vidal, leader of WWF’s global climate and energy practice and former President of COP20, joins with three former COP presidents in issuing a ‘call to arms’ as the COP24 UN climate summit opens in Katowice, Poland on Sunday.
